ZH: 鸵鸟是一种大型的鸟类。
EN: An ostrich is a large bird.
ZH: 鸵鸟无法飞行，但速度非常快。
EN: Ostriches cannot fly, but they can run very fast.
ZH: 鸵鸟的身体高大而强壮。
EN: Ostriches have tall and strong bodies.
ZH: 鸵鸟的脖子很长，可以伸展到很远的地方。
EN: Ostriches have long necks that can extend to a great distance.
ZH: 鸵鸟的眼睛很大而明亮。
EN: Ostriches have big and bright eyes.
ZH: 鸵鸟的脚有两趾，非常强壮。
EN: Ostriches have two toes on their feet, which are very strong.
ZH: 鸵鸟的声音像是响亮的咕噜声。
EN: The sound of an ostrich is like a loud rumble.
ZH: 鸵鸟的尾巴短小而柔软。
EN: Ostriches have short and soft tails.
ZH: 鸵鸟以植物和昆虫为食。
EN: Ostriches feed on plants and insects.
ZH: 鸵鸟在非洲的沙漠地带生活。
EN: Ostriches live in the desert areas of Africa.
ZH: 鸵鸟一次产卵多达20个。
EN: Ostriches can lay up to 20 eggs at once.
ZH: 鸵鸟用自己的翅膀遮住蛋来保暖。
EN: Ostriches use their wings to cover the eggs and keep them warm.
ZH: 鸵鸟的羽毛非常柔软而丰满。
EN: Ostrich feathers are very soft and fluffy.
ZH: 鸵鸟是世界上最大的鸟类。
EN: The ostrich is the largest bird in the world.
ZH: 鸵鸟通过踩在地上发出警报声来警戒。
EN: Ostriches give warning calls by stomping their feet on the ground.
ZH: 鸵鸟在繁殖季节会表现出攻击性。
EN: Ostriches can display aggression during the breeding season.
ZH: 鸵鸟的肉被人们用于食用。
EN: Ostrich meat is consumed by people.
ZH: 鸵鸟的皮革可以用来制作高级皮具。
EN: Ostrich leather is used to make high-end leather goods.
ZH: 鸵鸟的运动能力非常出色。
EN: Ostriches have excellent athletic abilities.
ZH: 鸵鸟的孵卵期约为40天。
EN: The incubation period for ostrich eggs is around 40 days.
